comments: Schofield (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Anunoby (TOR) and absorbs the contact.
Schofield (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by VanVleet (TOR).
Bertans (WAS) and Ibaka (TOR) make incidental contact as they make natural moves toward the rebound.
Lowry (TOR) makes contact with Smith's (WAS) arm and affects his ability to maintain control of the ball.
McCaw (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Beal (WAS) absorbs the contact.
Thomas (WAS) moves into Lowry (TOR) and delivers contact that affects his SQBR during his drive.
Anunoby (TOR) is drawn into the air and delivers body contact with Thomas (WAS) that affects his SQBR. The contact occurs prior to his upward shooting motion.
Lowry (TOR) gathers the ball and establishes his right foot as his pivot foot. Lowry then maintains his pivot foot.
Lowry (TOR) loses control of the ball prior to any incidental contact from Beal (WAS).
Schofield (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Anunoby (TOR) and absorbs the contact.
Beal (WAS) attempts to commit a take foul, but the marginal contact occurs after VanVleet (TOR) has released the ball during his pass.
Schofield (WAS) commits a take foul on VanVleet (TOR).
Lowry (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Beal (WAS).
Beal (WAS) commits a take foul on VanVleet (TOR).
